description: The Sarge dropped by for our weekly game of tic-tac-toe along with Evie as our playing surface. Rubberband brand tic- tac-toe is a win, win kinda game for me and the Sarge. Then I left the Sarge to his own devices for the rest of the shoot. There are some amazing visuals of the beautiful Evie in the tank scenes. Thanks for stopping by again you two!
title: Maya Matthews
